\id COL  
\h KOLOSI 
\toc1 Kolosi 
\toc2 Kolosi 
\toc3 Kolosi 
\mt1 Kolosi  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Aya Pol, Negur nẽ oroya bunem Kristus Jesus nẽ aposel wõ aun ado, neda turada Timoti adom,   
\p
\v 2 oun Kolosi taun, Negur nẽ fateul tamo kayau, Kristus bun momoiya turamã tar bun pas enei matotkeneik.  
\p Wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya, Tamada Negur bunem ã bun ibodõf.   
\s1 De Fiyẽya Ado Kosẽya  
\p
\v 3 Sain amã ã nigin kosẽ mauf bun, amã faimud neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ Tama, Negur de mafiyẽdig,  
\v 4 ere nigin, amã Kristus Jesus bun ãgenei momoiya ado, ã Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan nigin wauĩ laa fiya anĩ karĩ maun.  
\v 5 Ã mogo momoi nẽ od, biya od ã bun isin anĩ karĩg fen, ereb ã nigin saa ilun inon nigin wauĩ ise fen, momoiya ado wauĩ laa fiya anĩ wõ yen.  
\v 6 Sain ã biya od anĩ karĩg fen, Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya momoi bagai kelein sain anĩ bunem ilauf ganan, biya od anĩ ã atun age fen gen, teneub ganan bun, biya od enei faat yu ken, odugef.  
\v 7 Ã, nemã oboimã ferfer turamã Epafras bun keleĩ anĩ walegen, ĩ amã nawamã yaleya, Kristus nẽ kabĩ tamo dõ fiya biya,  
\v 8 agef fen, inimeg ãgenei Awa Uur bun wauĩ laa fiya nigin irokanaman.   
\p
\v 9 Age fiya nigin, sain amã ã nigin karĩ maun bunem isif ganan, amã ã nigin Negur kosẽ mafiye ken, uur nẽ kisi biya ado kisi fokõya ganan bunem Negur nẽ oroya nigin keleĩ aura yeĩf nigin to fiyẽya to matorõdig.  
\v 10 Age mafe fen, amã, ã Odug nẽ oroya bun ubodõg fen, ereb ereb ganan bun Odug wau al fouf nẽ anĩ ago gouf nigin kosẽ maudig: faat biya kabĩ biya ganan bun yũf nigin, Negur nigin keleĩ, ã bun odugouf nigin,  
\v 11 yogon fula fiya medeĩya nẽ megeir bunem megeir ganan ifeneĩ di, ã ereb ereb ganan bun, feseya sã megeir bagai ufaragauf nigin, agef fen, wauĩ kulĩya ado,  
\v 12 Tamada ĩ, ã lalan nẽ tano bun Negur nẽ tamo kayau neid akor weim walogouf nigin age fen anĩ, de wiyẽgouf nigin kosẽ maudig.  
\v 13 Ere nigin, ĩ ada gugum nẽ megeir bun yalelnada fen, in Naal Negurem ĩ nigin wau laa fedig anĩ nẽ tano bun gei fada irou isidan.  
\v 14 Ĩ Naal bun ada kel yaledan, neda mosor nigin weder tu kelen.   
\s1 Kristus Ĩ Ereb Ereb Ganan Wal Fiya  
\p
\v 15 Kristus ĩ, Negur ada to tailef anĩ nẽ malakanon, ĩ Negur nẽ kesu matu, ereb ereb inodin ganan anĩ nẽ mudur inenen.  
\v 16 Are, Kristus ĩ bunem ereb ereb ganan inodin, ereb ereb saa ilun ifaredif ado tenebur ein ifaredif, ereb ereb tailef ado to tailef, king, megeir, uyu iroudiya be, yeneid adodo; ereb ereb ganan Kristus bunem Kristus nigin ye fen, inodin.  
\v 17 Kristus ĩ ereb ereb ganan wõya sã mog, ibodon, agef fen, ĩ bun ereb ereb ganan ifaref.  
\v 18 Ĩ bouwa are sios, ĩ yogo anĩ nẽ mudur. Ĩ gariya, tamo gare den bun tamal uyulil kel fã yen, are ereb ereb ganan bun ĩ mudur ibodõf nigin age fen.  
\v 19 Negur ĩ yogon kisi feleya bagai anĩ ganan, Kristus bun ibodõf nigin oro fen,  
\v 20 ĩ Kristus nẽ naud aa tetek bun fi felen anĩ bunem maror ino fen, Kristus bunem ereb ereb ganan tenebur ifaredif be, saa ilun ifaredif, ĩ geid komo difouf nigin oron.   
\p
\v 21 Uruwa bun, ã Negur nigin gerõ ufareg fen, ãgenei tobonunã sane bunem, ãgenei kisi bun Negur nigin kiwai ubodõgen.  
\v 22 Anĩ ere gama, Negur ĩ, Kristus nẽ bouwam laa bunem, yogon lo fiya bun ã fateul, amuyẽ sã, od sã ineneĩf nigin ĩ geid komo yein.  
\v 23 Ã ãgenei momoiya tobol ge fen, feseya sã totol ufareg fen, biya od karĩ gen sain bun wauĩ iseya walegen anĩ bun to ulegef usigef gouf are, agog wõ gouf. Biya od enei are, ereb ereb ganan saa farumen ifaref anidi bun kurõ fesin, agef fen, aya Pol biya od anĩ nẽ kabĩ tamo wõ aun.   
\s1 Pol Sios Nigin Kabĩ Totol Yalen  
\p
\v 24 Gama aya ã nigin darau alef anĩ nigin wau al fef, age afe fen, Kristus ĩ yogon bouwa sios nigin darau yalen bun fau to kisi felef anĩ kisi falauf nigin, aya bouwaum darau anĩ ale di, kisi falauf.  
\v 25 Aya Negur nẽ od anĩ kisi feleya bagai afeneĩf nigin, Negur kabĩ ifanan anĩ nẽ kabĩ tamo wõ aun.  
\v 26 Negur nẽ od are ĩ waa, kulunem ibor isin ganan bun iminẽyan ibodon anĩ, gama Negur nẽ momoiya tamo kayau bun yaor fen.  
\v 27 Negur nẽ tamo kayau bun, Negurem waa enei nẽ fula fiya medeĩya barikã anĩ naig be fiya anĩ, haiden atun yaor fouf nigin wau iron, waa are Kristus ã namein ibodok, anĩ nẽ fula fiya medeĩya nigin wau iseya anĩ.   
\p
\v 28 Amã ĩ nigin kurõ mafalaisi, tamo kayau ganan wedereid maroud fen, kisi biya ganan bun, tamo kayau ganan mafelnẽdidig, are amã tamo kayau ganan Kristus bun, kisi feleya bagai manenẽdiyouf nigin age mafef.  
\v 29 Enei kisi falauf nigin, aya kabĩ totol alef, yogon megeir aya nameun ibod ken, kabĩ totol yalef anim aya gunĩ auf.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Aya ã nigin, idi Laodisia taun difaref anidi nigin ado, idi aya to bagai dileyaf anidi ganan nigin, naig afe gunĩ auf anĩ, ã keleĩ youf nigin orouf.  
\v 2 Neu kisi bagai are, idi waud alese di, wau laa fiya bunem waud katõ difouf, age fe di, idi kisi fokõ feleya nigin keleĩ barikãf, anĩ bunem, idi Negur nẽ waa keleĩ youf, are Kristus.  
\v 3 Ĩ bun kisi biya ado keleĩ nẽ safina biya ganan inokon ibodok.  
\v 4 Aya taka nem meleĩ yaleya od biyai biyai bunem to idegneĩf nigin enei arokeneik.  
\v 5 Momoi, aya bouwaum ã geid to tabodok, anĩ ere, aya uur bun ã geid tabod ken, ã naig be ge tutuk ufareg fen, ãgenei Kristus bun momoiya naig be fe megeir ifaref anĩ, ileya nigin wau irok.   
\s1 Tamo Nẽ Lo Wal Fe Fen, Kristus Bun Mata Ibodõya  
\p
\v 6 Ã Kristus Jesus ãgenei Odug walegen, anĩ nigin, ã ĩ bun mata ubodõgouf.  
\v 7 Ĩ bun warei urarãg fen, fõ kare gen walesagauf, ã difelnein kilei, ãgenei momoiya bun megeir ge fen, de fiyẽya anĩ ã bun ise gogũ fouf.   
\p
\v 8 Taka nem ã, tamo nẽ idegẽya keleĩ kaũ sã bunem to gurar yeĩ irouleyeĩf nigin lo walagauf, are Kristus dõ fiya ban, tamo nẽ tobonunã ado tenebur enei nẽ tobonunã dõ fiya nigin.   
\p
\v 9 Ere nigin, Kristus bun Negur nẽ kisi feleya bagai ganan bouwa bun ibodok.  
\v 10 Agef fen, ã Kristus bun kisi feleya bagai ifenein, Kristus ĩ megeir ganan ado yeneid adodo ganan neid mudur.  
\v 11 Ĩ bun ãg mulũ ulegen, are tamo imam mulũ bun ineneĩya sã, anĩ ere, mosor nẽ oroya yaleleya nigin, Kristusem mulũ bun inenein.  
\v 12 Ã, ĩ geid naan yaleya bun mũ yei ken, Negur ĩ laa bun tamal Kristus kel turĩ fiyen anĩ nẽ megeir bun, ãgenei momoiya bunem ĩ geid kel turĩ yein.   
\p
\v 13 Sain ã, ãgenei mosor nigin ado ãgenei mosor nẽ oroya nigin mulũ ileya sã nigin, laa bun ufareg mog, Negur ĩ, ã Kristus geid kel turĩ yein. Ĩ neda mosor adok nigin weder tu kelen.  
\v 14 Ĩ lo nẽ ĩtãfiya itotoya, are ada weteda kiwai ibodon anĩ isasalen, ĩ anĩ yalel fen, aa tetek bun yun.  
\v 15 Agef fen, ĩ, megeir adodo yeneid adodo neid totol ganan, ye farumen gõ fel fen, Kristus nẽ aa tetek bunem kusĩ bun idi wal fedin anĩ dilouf nigin, ganan meleid bun yaor fen.   
\p
\v 16 Anĩ nigin, ã saaf be naan wãgauf, uub sifa naa fire fire be, ogõ mata sigigi fiya naa be, Sabat naa\f + \fr 2:16  \ft Sabat naa anĩ, Juda neid uub nẽ naa.\f* to dõ gouf bun, taka nem to es yeĩf.  
\v 17 Eneidi are, ereb fau isiyouf nẽ malakanon. Anĩ ere, ereb momoi bagai are Kristus bun fotou fiyauf.  
\v 18 Aib taka ĩ, mala yaleya nigin wau yukesileya ado engel yeneid yaleseya nigin wau al fef anim, ã mala solo walogouf anĩ to wal yeĩf. Tamo age fiya ĩ ereb ilen anĩ nigin nenerĩ meluk dir fe fen, yogon bouwa nẽ oroya anim, gariya sã fagã yedig.  
\v 19 Ĩ bouwa nẽ mudur Kristus anĩ folõ fel fen ifaren, mudur are Kristus, ĩ bunem bouwa ganan tuwa katõ fiya ado dirumunã anidim disennẽ di, katõ fel ifar fen, Negur yogo age fe di, odugedig.   
\p
\v 20 Ã Kristus geid tenebur enei nẽ tobonunã bun laa yein, age fiyauf are, ere nigin anĩ ã fau anĩ nẽ gen ufareg fen, yogon ĩtãfiya eig fiya farumen ufaregef,  
\v 21 “Ã to uroug! Ã to kobũg uleg! Ã to dorõg uleg!”?  
\v 22 Enei ganan are, kabĩ wenẽge di, sa kalauf, ere nigin, idi tamo nẽ ĩtãfiya ado tai fiya dogol.  
\v 23 Momoi, ĩtãfiya age age fediya are, dogo neid kisim seli kulõ fiya, dogo neid idegẽya waud yukesileya ado, dogo neid bouweid kafĩ fiya ifenẽya bun, kisi biya gen ulegedig, anĩ ere, idi bouwa nẽ oroya lai fesileya nigin kisi feleya sã.   
\c 3  
\s1 Fateul Ibodõya Nẽ Faded Fiya  
\p
\v 1 Age fiya nigin, ã mogo Kristus geid keg fã gen nigin, ãgenei wauĩ ereb ereb ilun nẽ nigin, Kristus Negur ima biyalẽ ibodok nẽ an, unogouf.  
\v 2 Ãgenei kisi ereb ereb ilun nẽ nigin unogouf, ereb ereb tenebur nẽ nigin sã.  
\v 3 Ere nigin, ã gareg fen, ãgenei mata gama Kristus geid Negur bun inokon.  
\v 4 Kristus ĩ ãgenei mata, ĩ wõ youf sain bun, ãg ĩ geid fula fiya medeĩya bun wõ gouf.   
\p
\v 5 Anĩ nigin, ereb ereb ãgenei tenebur nẽ oroya nẽ anĩ udenkesig: noli tobonunã, amuyẽ tobonunã, noli kisi, oroya sesen ado, safina musei youf nigin ima su lai fe fen sũ we fiya (are idegẽya waitou seli yabiya).  
\v 6 Eig fediya nigin, Negur nẽ didi isif.  
\v 7 Ã uruwa ubodõgen, naab enei bun uyõgen.  
\v 8 Anĩ ere, ã gama naab eig fediya, wau saneya, didi iseya, tobonunã sesen inoya, dumen od irõya ado, sigoreĩ bun od sesen wogõya, anĩ ganan utorõgouf.  
\v 9 Ã abob to udegnẽgouf, ere nigin, ãgenei bouweĩ nẽ oroya tubu yogon tobonunã ado uraileg fen,  
\v 10 oroya mata ufonũgen, are Negur nẽ malakanon nigin keleĩ bun mata falei yeĩdig.  
\v 11 Ein baban, Grik tamo be Juda tamo, mulũ ileya be mulũ ileya sã, yaũ tamo be tamo kuĩ gen, ferfer be kafĩ fiya sã tamo gen, fire fire to ibodok, anĩ ere, Kristus ĩ anĩ ganan, ĩ ganan anĩ namedin ibodok.   
\p
\v 12 Anĩ nigin, ã tamo kayau Negurem igirnein, fateul ado Negur nẽ oboi tar nigin, wau yũya, tobonunã biya, wau yukesileya, molol ado, kaisã to seyeya anĩ ufonũgouf.  
\v 13 Molol ufareg fen, abob nigin morõ faali gouf, agog fen, ã atun abob ereb morõ ibodõf anĩ nigin wedereĩ tu kalauf. Odug ãgenei mosor nigin weder tu kelen gen, ãg mosor nigin wedereĩ tu kalauf.  
\v 14 Agog fen, enei ganan teten, wauĩ laa fiya ufonũgouf, anim ereb ereb ganan tekelei guf irouwauf.   
\p
\v 15 Kristus nẽ wau inosiya ãgenei wauĩ bun utorõg len, ulum irouwauf, ere nigin, ã bouwa tekelei bun wau inosiya bun iweignein. Agog fen, Negur de wiyẽgouf.  
\v 16 Utorõg len, Kristus nẽ od fatuk bagai ã namein ibodõ di, ã kisi biya ganan bunem abob ufelnẽdig fen, abob weder urougauf, agog fen, od Negur nẽ Itotoya Sam bun ibodok, Negur yana yaleseya seg ado, uur nẽ seg, ãgenei wauĩ bun Negur de fiyẽya ado walogouf.  
\v 17 Agog fen, ereb ã ago gef, od bun be kabĩ yaleya bun, anĩ ganan Odug Jesus yana bun agog fen, ĩ bunem Dei Negur de wiyẽgouf.   
\s1 Momoiya Tamo Kayau Ibor Mata Ibodõya Nẽ Faded Fiya  
\p
\v 18 Kayau, ãgenei tamo farumen ubodõgouf, are Odug nẽ lo fiya bun biya bagai.   
\p
\v 19 Tamo, ãgenei aiweĩ tar nigin wauĩ laaf fen, idi waud morõ to wenẽdigouf.   
\p
\v 20 Kesu, ã ereb ereb ganan bun sineĩ temeĩ tar sigoreid dõ gouf, anim Odug wau al fouf.   
\p
\v 21 Tama, ã gereneĩ tar to waud saneya wenẽdigouf, ago gouf, idi agogon de fen, waud to al fouf.   
\p
\v 22 Ferfer, ã ereb ereb ganan bun, ãgenei marau tenebur enei nẽ sigoreid dõ gouf, idi meledin dogol idi biya difamãf ya bunem meleid yaleya nigin dogol to ago gouf, anĩ ere, ã wauĩ momoi nẽ ado Odug nigin anini ge fen, ago gouf.  
\v 23 Ereb ago gef ganan, wauĩ adok iro ken, ago gouf, tamo nigin sã, Odug nigin kabĩ alef ge fen, kabĩ walogouf,  
\v 24 ere nigin, ã keleĩ, ã Odug bun tamal in akor mala solo walogouf. Are Odug Kristus anĩ ã aruna walekenẽgef.  
\v 25 Aib taka ĩ sane age fouf, yogon sane age fiya nigin mala solo sane yalouf, ere nigin, an anĩ kinau ya sã.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Marau ã, ãgenei ferfer ereb madur ado biya anĩ wenẽdigouf, ere nigin, ã keleĩ, ãg saa ilun ãgenei Marau ibodok.   
\s1 Faded Fiya Tunĩ  
\p
\v 2 Kosẽya anĩ totol uroug, lo weleg fen, Negur de wiyẽgouf.  
\v 3 Agog fen, amã nigineg kosẽ gouf, are Negur amã od wogõ mauf nigin bobog kã fel kanamã di, amã Kristus nẽ waa kurõ mafalaisiyouf nigin kosẽ gouf, anĩ nigin aya kalabus bun abodok.  
\v 4 Negur aya biya od wogõ auf nigin ifanan anĩ, sã yaor kurõ afalaisiyouf nigin kosẽ gouf.  
\v 5 Ereb tamo kayau serẽ temeleid bun ago gou fenẽ, kisi biya ado ago gouf. Sain biya ã nigin wõ youf ganan to sekil gouf.  
\v 6 Ãgenei wogõya sain bun ganan wau ifenẽya barikãf, od karĩya biya dogol wogõ gouf, anĩ bunem, ã, tamo kayau ganan naig be fe solof irokenẽdiya nigin keleĩ youf.   
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Aanya  
\p
\v 7 Tikikusem aya nigin od ganan wogõ yeĩf. Ĩ neu turau oboiyou, kabĩ tamo dõ fiya biya fen, Odug bun kabĩ turau.  
\v 8 Aya, ĩ, ã bun enei nigin bagai sur afiyek, are ã, amã naig ma mafaref anĩ keleĩ di, anĩ bunem ĩ ãgenei wauĩ yalesauf nigin, age afef.  
\v 9 Ĩ Onesimus ado disiyouf, Onesimus ĩ neda turada dõ fiya biya oboida, ĩ ãgenei taka. Idi ereb ereb ganan ein agef wõ yef anĩ dirokeneĩf.   
\p
\v 10 Neu kalabus turau Aristakus, ã bun yogon aanya sur fef, Mak, Banabas ne tam, ĩg agef aanya sur fef. (Ã ĩ nigin faded fiya walegen. Ĩ ã garan isiyouf are, ã ĩ walogouf.)  
\v 11 Jesus ĩ yana taka Jastus dedig, ĩg aanya sur fef. Negur nẽ tano nigin neu kabĩ tamo turau tar atun, idi dogol anĩ Juda temeleid. Age de fen, idi momoi bagai de fen, neu wau dalesen.  
\v 12 Epafras ĩ ãgenei taka, Kristus Jesus nẽ kabĩ tamo, ã bun aanya sur fef. Ĩ faimud kosẽya bun ã nigin totol inodig, are ã Negur nẽ oroya ganan bun, kisi feleya bagai ado momoiya odug bun totol ufaragauf nigin age fef.  
\v 13 Aya, ĩ, ã nigin, idi Laodisia taun difaref anidi nigin ado, idi Hierapolis taun difaref anidi nigin kabĩ totol yaledig anĩ, sã ĩ nigin kurõ afesif.  
\v 14 Nemã oboimã dokta Luk ado Demas aanya sur difef.  
\v 15 Tureĩ tar Laodisia taun dibodok anidi bun ado, Nimfa ado sios yogon fõ bun guru difef anidi bun, neu aanya wenẽdigouf.   
\p
\v 16 Pas enei uweseg le di, Laodisia sios buneg diwesauf, abag, Laodisia tamal paseg uwesagauf.   
\p
\v 17 Akipus urokenẽg, “Õ Odug bun kabĩ walen anĩ, el wo udikalauf nigin karĩ walauf.”   
\p
\v 18 Aya, Polem aanya enei imaum bagai atotof. Aya kalabus bun abodok anĩ karĩ walagauf. Wau ifenẽya ã ado ibodõf.   